Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我将成为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:43.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,这就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:53.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你为什么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
